## 6. Overlay de FPS (MangoHud)

```bash
# ~/.config/MangoHud/MangoHud.conf
fps
frame_timing
gpu_temp
cpu_temp
ram
vram
position=top-left
```

Uso: `mangohud game` ou `mangohud %command%` no Steam.

